====== Joshua D. Drake ======

  * Major Contributor to PostgreSQL.org
  * SPI Liaison for PostgreSQL.org
  * President PostgreSQL.us
  * Lead Consultant Command Prompt, Inc. oldest PostgreSQL dedicated consultancy in the United States

===== PITR made easy =====

A 45 minute (or so) talk on implementing PITRTools, a suite of Open Source software that makes PITR implementation easy with PostgreSQL. The software includes arbitrary alerts and failover capability.



